---
title: Nan's Beef, Mushroom & Hidden Veggie Pasta with Parmesan Cheese
description: Twirl your fork around this beef and veggie penne and you'll quickly discover how easy and tasty it is to eat! Served with a creamy mushroom and tomato-based sauce and topped with Parmesan cheese, it's melt-in-your-mouth delicious!
